<p>Because sometimes remembering past failures and ugly design attemtps is just as helpful as completing successful projects, this page logs a few of my own failed/aborted/bad projects.</p>

<h3 id="handcrafted-led-matrix">Handcrafted LED matrix</h3>

<p>A 16x8 homemade LED matrix I built while experimenting with Arduino and MAX7219.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/MuseumOfHorrors/LED_display_board_front.png" alt="LED display board front" /></p>

<p>You donâ€™t want to know how long it took me to solder &amp; check everythingâ€¦which was extremely pointless given that a pre-made LED matrix of similar
dimensions can be bought for a few bucks.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/MuseumOfHorrors/LED_display_board_back.png" alt="LED display board back" /></p>

